[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":186},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fvscode\u002F20200312\u002F457161302\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fvscode\u002F20200312\u002F457161302\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fvscode\u002F20200312\u002F457161302\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fvscode\u002F20200312\u002F457161302\u002F":163,"related:\u002Fvscode\u002F20200312\u002F457161302\u002F":172},"\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2020\u002F03\u002F12\u002Fvscode-1-43-syntax-highlight-issue\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":147,"date":148,"description":18,"extension":149,"lang":150,"meta":151,"navigation":152,"path":153,"readingMinutes":154,"seo":155,"standalone":156,"stem":157,"tags":158,"tldr":160,"updated":160,"url":161,"__hash__":162},"content\u002FVSCode\u002FVisual Studio Code(VSCode) -1-43-高亮問題.md","Visual Studio Code(VSCode) 1.43 高亮問題","457161302",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":141},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,34,41,57,86,94,99,102,108,111,118,121,137],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"這幾天 Visual Studio Code(VSCode) 更新成了 1.43，但卻發生高亮不太正常?!不知道是刻意改的還是不正常的關係，所以這一篇紀錄一下該如何解決。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"問題點",[16,23,24,25,29,30,33],{},"前天還昨天 Visual Studio Code(VSCode) 更新到 1.43 之後，舉凡 ",[26,27,28],"code",{},"console.log()","、",[26,31,32],{},"import"," 等等都變成下面這張圖的顏色",[16,35,36],{},[37,38],"img",{"alt":39,"src":40},"高亮","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-03-12%2010.25.35.png",[16,42,43,44,51,52,56],{},"看起來像是另一種主題，後來找到 ",[45,46,50],"a",{"href":47,"rel":48},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fmicrosoft\u002Fvscode\u002Fissues\u002F92360",[49],"nofollow","這一篇"," 以及 ",[45,53,50],{"href":54,"rel":55},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fmicrosoft\u002Fvscode\u002Fissues\u002F92308",[49]," 討論串，只需要開啟 setting 並加入以下設定值就可以恢復原本的高亮",[58,59,64],"pre",{"className":60,"code":61,"language":62,"meta":63,"style":63},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\"editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled\": false,\n","js","",[26,65,66],{"__ignoreMap":63},[67,68,71,75,79,83],"span",{"class":69,"line":70},"line",1,[67,72,74],{"class":73},"sTRMh","\"editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled\"",[67,76,78],{"class":77},"sMAXC",": ",[67,80,82],{"class":81},"sCcAr","false",[67,84,85],{"class":77},",\n",[16,87,88,89,93],{},"或者是在 setting 中搜尋 ",[90,91,92],"strong",{},"Semantic Highlighting"," 並取消打勾即可。",[16,95,96],{},[37,97],{"alt":92,"src":98},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-03-12%2010.49.50.png",[16,100,101],{},"前鬼我還你原樣！",[16,103,104],{},[37,105],{"alt":106,"src":107},"恢復原本主題高亮","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-03-12%2010.24.23.png",[16,109,110],{},"因為這個問題害我噴了一個晚上重新安裝 VSCode 並停用所有擴充套件，一度我還以為是不是更新了主題高亮，所以還嘗試替換成其他主題結果狀況還是一樣。",[16,112,113,114,117],{},"依照上面討論串的說法就是官方在更新 1.43 之後將語法突出這個功能預設改成了 ",[26,115,116],{},"true","，所以才會導致這個問題發生。",[12,119,120],{"id":120},"參考文獻",[122,123,124,131],"ul",{},[125,126,127],"li",{},[45,128,130],{"href":47,"rel":129},[49],"Enable JS\u002FTS language features change the assets of VS Code",[125,132,133],{},[45,134,136],{"href":54,"rel":135},[49],"February 2020 (version 1.43) update broke js syntax highlighting",[138,139,140],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":63,"searchDept